      "span_text": "A recent elegant study suggested that ubiquitylation and Brca1 are required for this replisome dissolution at ICLs, but the specific substrate of this ubiquitylation is not yet known.  If polyubiquitylation of Mcm7 is indeed essential for efficient DNA damage response and repair, its significance in maintenance of genomic stability and cancer development will be even greater."
